properties.areaDesc: Bays and Waterways from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas; Coastal waters from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas out 20 NM
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued January 14 at 5:25PM CST by NWS Corpus Christi TX
properties.description:
Moist onshore flow will continue to produce fog along the bays and
waterways as well as the nearshore waters south of Port Aransas
this evening. Visibilities will generally range from 2 to 4
nautical miles, with patchy dense fog of 1 nautical mile or less
at times.

Mariners over the Bays and Nearshore Coastal Waters within 20
nautical miles offshore are urged to prepare for rapidly changing
visibilities.

NWSheadline: PATCHY DENSE FOG THROUGH THE NIGHT
